These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: electronic, country, classical, hip-hop, disco, punk, techno
7 different pets are kept: mouse, guinea-pig, rat, cat, bird, goat, goldfish
 1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 2. the owner of the bird is the fan of hip-hop##1
 3. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of punk##1
 4. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 5. the fan of classical is in the middle##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
 7. the fan of disco is the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the fan of electronic is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 9. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the owner of the cat is on the left of the fan of classical##1
11. the fan of techno is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Music-Genre           | disco | hip-hop | country | classical | electronic | punk | techno |
| Pet   | mouse    | bird   | cat      | goat | rat    | guinea-pig    | goldfish         |

