.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, vegafina, pall-mall, oliveros, havana, tiparillo, aristoff
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: biathlon, tennis, skiing, ice-hockey, surfing, golf, badminton
 1. the person who's sport is surfing is the oliveros-smoker##1
 2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 3. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
 4. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 5. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
 7. the person who's sport is surfing is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
 9. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
10. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Cigar          | dannemann | vegafina | havana | oliveros | tiparillo | aristoff | pall-mall |
| Sport   | tennis      | skiing   | ice-hockey   | surfing      | biathlon       | badminton       | golf     |

