.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, skydiving, card-games, board-games, fishing, traveling, filmmaking
House: palace, colonial, victorian, townhouse, cottage, futuristic, tower
 1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the tower house##1
 3. the colonial house is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 5. the palace house is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 6. the victorian house is on the right of the colonial house##1
 7. the colonial house is on the left of the victorian house##1
 8. the colonial house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 9. the person who's hobby is traveling is the townhouse house##1
10. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the palace house##1
11. the townhouse house is in the middle##1
12. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Hobby   | skydiving | fishing     | card-games  | traveling       | baking       | filmmaking  | board-games   |
| House    | futuristic  | palace | tower | townhouse | colonial | victorian | cottage |

