 5. the tower house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 6. the cottage house is on the far left##1
 7. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the cottage house##1
 8. the craftsman house is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
 9. the craftsman house is the person who likes emerald##1
10. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the futuristic house##1
11. the person who likes blue is the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
