.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: train, roller, motorbike, bus, quad-bike, skateboard, boat
7 different games are played: canasta, monopoly, mah-jongg, go, poker, scrabble, bridge
 1. the person driving the roller is the person playing bridge##1
 2. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 3. the person playing scrabble is in the middle##1
 4. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 5. the person playing poker is the person driving the skateboard##1
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 7. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 8. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 9. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person playing poker##1
10. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Transport   | roller | motorbike | skateboard     | bus | boat | quad-bike | train |
| Game     | bridge   | mah-jongg    | poker | scrabble     | canasta         | go     | monopoly        |

