7 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, cain, montecristo, prince, oliveros, blend, havana
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is the prince-smoker##1
 4. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
 6. the havana-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 7. the swisher-smoker is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is in the middle##1
 9. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
10. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Birthday   | july  | january | may | june | december     | october | march |
| Cigar     | blend | prince      | havana | montecristo    | oliveros | cain   | swisher  |

